{"tid":2096720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國外交部籲在加公民注意治安　謹慎前往當地","createTime":"2020-07-06T09:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T10:31:27.000Z","uid":60281,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"28a02634836d4539846d1c4112a021950271df2c","tid":2096720,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國外交部領事司在微信公眾號表示，加拿大近期頻繁發生執法部門暴力執法問題，並引發多宗遊行示威活動，外交部及中國駐加使領館提醒中國公民密切關注當地治安，近期謹慎前往當地。<br />\n<br />\n當局又指，中國國民如在當地遇上緊急情況，需要及時聯繫中國駐加使領館尋求協助。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536090-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536090-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=0630f836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536090-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=af2355de\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536090-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5c0ac5fd3ec78020c3028c188bdd15024d41da34","tid":2096720,"uid":202876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"應該撤僑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快"},{"pid":"111adae257479c78d739595c524892c9152f771e","tid":2096720,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"中國應該取消與加拿大嘅引渡條約以作反制"},{"pid":"83e369be2d9635c5365b196bac4442b6bd52ecb1","tid":2096720,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"第三世界話人地好危險"},{"pid":"cccd891d286b880c7d5ca714e8e898de2e21e360","tid":2096720,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"我地要驚d當地小粉紅同埋CSSA成員好過喇"},{"pid":"a8f02664e71e1766c21bbc131660b219517ba0a